Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:14.97,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}明晰梦，又叫做自觉梦、觉醒梦。\N做梦时可以自觉地行动的梦。\N梦中发生的事能根据人的意识改变。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十月二日  傍晚五时二十五分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姐姐也没起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比往常更早地离开了那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我曾经在那附近的天空中飞翔过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我登上神社的石阶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像  看到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里做坏事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被松尾大人责骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（注：松尾大人，日本酒酿造的神，被供奉在酿酒的店里）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我什么也没有做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐  今天也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为邻居家的大爷说今晚还想喝点酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿的那是糙米酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是今晚再喝点的话  血压就能降下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  其实就是健康饮料之类的东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长说要用明年酿的酒准备正规的酒场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快点把明年的酒场筹备起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐  你用香水了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可能是洗发水的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酿酒的时候我是绝对不会用香水的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  你的鼻子可真灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是老板的嫡子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  味道不怎么好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喝惯了就会觉得好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起码…我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年要开始正规地酿造糙米酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她一开始好像不是很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来邻居家大爷身体好起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就开始有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说九月份之后有很多转校生要来了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山那边的工厂似乎有所行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是希望我继承家业的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是讨厌酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是…我小时候偷偷喝了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点恶心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了你那代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道这里的水还能不能用来酿酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该由姐姐她继承的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}很伤脑筋吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  能借我抄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对转校生要亲切些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管  跟别人说去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎么一副没睡醒的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚根本没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  看  大神居然来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B班的大神？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好像已经两周没来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  老师来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不坐到位子上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快坐好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}…逐渐变得明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}…教科书53页  有好好看着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也来了这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  神社背后有这样一条路的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  只是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是在梦里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦魇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我说  那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}别淘气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊  这是体罚  体罚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}德永
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要是出手打他你就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是啦是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古森  今天放学后来一下校长室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来做随堂测试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是A班的古森太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…还真的叫太郎啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是转校到B班的中岛匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次到我家去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多事情想请教你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说吧  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  古森同学你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个月开始临床心理老师换人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是东京大学的平田笃司老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个月开始负责你的心理咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的心理老师也是使用这房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去职员室了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了叫我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的风景可真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有「日本」风味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有和以前的心理老师交接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是经常在白天感到睡意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的  时常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你把梦都记录下来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都录在磁带里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后能让我听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不愿意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须先好好整理下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一年前发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是让古森同学你感到痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[水天町2名儿童被绑架]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[犯人因发生事故丧生]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[在警察的眼皮底下……赎金交付失败]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[2名儿童失踪]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[父母的愿望落空]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:02.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[2儿童被绑架事件：行踪不明4日后  弟弟太郎安全获救]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大神同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一次见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从东京搬过来的中岛匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以直接叫你的名字「信」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  还真够烦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常有人这样说我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我性格就是这样  没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  平田老师…您会用催眠疗法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  一旦被催眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忘记了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能记起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想回忆起来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丧失了部分记忆  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对催眠疗法不是特别认同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催眠有时会出现自己捏造的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回忆起什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校嘛  我只有兴致来了才会去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再缠着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我有事想问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于A班的太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你很憎恨他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和十一年前信你的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了么  只是想问问你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天白天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不理不睬的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说只要训练一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就可以自由的在梦中行动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是弗朗西斯·克里克的梦的解析认为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:42.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（注：弗朗西斯·克里克(Francis Crick)，英国分子生物学家。\N在DNA分子双螺旋结构的发现，\N以及在揭开生物遗传信息秘密方面作出贡献。）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦不过是把记录在大脑新皮质中的无意义记忆消除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.71,0:24:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其本身是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.12,0:24:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于克里克来说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.35,0:24:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识不过是一种发生于脑内的40赫兹共鸣现象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:25:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦  梦的形态  梦的世界  幽世
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.96,0:25:04.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\an5\pos(640,475)}--眼动脱敏与再加工疗法--
